---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Building a Personal CRM in Notion (Free Template)" 
  description="Track job applications, freelance clients, and networking contacts in one place. Includes my actual template and workflow."
>
  <article class="blog-post">
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Post Header -->
      <header class="post-header fade-in-up">
        <div class="post-meta">
          <span class="post-tag">Tutorial</span>
          <span class="post-date">May 2, 2026</span>
          <span class="post-read-time">• 10 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1>Building a Personal CRM in Notion (Free Template)</h1>
        <p class="post-subtitle">
          How I track 40+ contacts, 15 job applications, and 3 freelance clients in one simple Notion database. Template included, no coding required.
        </p>
      </header>

      <!-- Template Preview -->
      <div class="template-preview fade-in-up stagger-1">
        <div class="preview-badge">
          <span class="badge-icon">📥</span>
          <span class="badge-text">Free Template Included</span>
        </div>
        <div class="preview-content">
          <div class="preview-visual">
            <div class="mock-database">
              <div class="db-header">
                <div class="db-title">My Network</div>
                <div class="db-stats">
                  <span>43 contacts</span>
                  <span>•</span>
                  <span>12 follow-ups</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="db-rows">
                <div class="db-row">
                  <span class="row-name">Sarah Chen</span>
                  <span class="row-tag active">Active</span>
                  <span class="row-date">Follow up: May 10</span>
                </div>
                <div class="db-row">
                  <span class="row-name">Tech Startup Co.</span>
                  <span class="row-tag interview">Interview</span>
                  <span class="row-date">Next: May 12</span>
                </div>
                <div class="db-row">
                  <span class="row-name">John Smith</span>
                  <span class="row-tag archived">Archived</span>
                  <span class="row-date">Last: Mar 15</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="preview-cta">
            <h3>What You'll Get</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>✅ Pre-built Notion database with all properties</li>
              <li>✅ 4 custom views (Active, Follow-ups, Job Search, Archive)</li>
              <li>✅ Email templates for follow-ups</li>
              <li>✅ Step-by-step setup video (coming soon)</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://notion.so/templates/your-template" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">
              Duplicate Template (Free) →
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="post-content">
        <section class="content-section fade-in-up stagger-2">
          <h2>Why You Need a Personal CRM</h2>
          <p>
            As a student, I'm constantly meeting people: professors, alumni, recruiters, freelance clients, fellow students. 
            Before this system, I'd lose track of conversations, miss follow-ups, and forget important details.
          </p>

          <div class="problem-solution">
            <div class="problem">
              <h3>😫 The Problem</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Business cards pile up with no system</li>
                <li>LinkedIn connections go nowhere</li>
                <li>Forget to follow up after coffee chats</li>
                <li>Can't remember who introduced you to whom</li>
                <li>Job application status scattered across email</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="solution">
              <h3>✅ The Solution</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>One central database for all contacts</li>
                <li>Automatic follow-up reminders</li>
                <li>Track conversation history</li>
                <li>Link contacts to opportunities</li>
                <li>Visual pipeline for job/client status</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="callout callout-success">
            <strong>Real Results:</strong> Since building this (3 months ago), I've:
            <ul>
              <li>Landed 2 freelance clients through warm intros</li>
              <li>Got 1 interview from a follow-up I would have forgotten</li>
              <li>Maintained relationships with 15+ people I otherwise would have lost touch with</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section fade-in-up stagger-3">
          <h2>CRM Structure: What to Track</h2>
          
          <div class="structure-grid">
            <div class="structure-card">
              <h3>📋 Basic Info</h3>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Name:</strong> Full name</li>
                <li><strong>Company/Organization:</strong> Where they work</li>
                <li><strong>Title:</strong> Their role</li>
                <li><strong>Email:</strong> Contact info</li>
                <li><strong>LinkedIn:</strong> Profile link</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="structure-card">
              <h3>🏷️ Categories</h3>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Type:</strong> Job lead, Client, Mentor, Peer, Recruiter</li>
                <li><strong>Status:</strong> Active, Pending, Closed, Archived</li>
                <li><strong>Priority:</strong> High, Medium, Low</li>
                <li><strong>Source:</strong> How you met (LinkedIn, Event, Referral)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="structure-card">
              <h3>📅 Timeline</h3>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>First Contact:</strong> When you met</li>
                <li><strong>Last Contact:</strong> Last interaction</li>
                <li><strong>Next Follow-up:</strong> Reminder date</li>
                <li><strong>Frequency:</strong> How often to check in</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="structure-card">
              <h3>📝 Context</h3>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Notes:</strong> Conversation highlights</li>
                <li><strong>Interests:</strong> Their hobbies/passions</li>
                <li><strong>How I Can Help:</strong> Value you can provide</li>
                <li><strong>Next Steps:</strong> What to do next</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section fade-in-up stagger-4">
          <h2>Step-by-Step Build Guide</h2>

          <div class="build-timeline">
            <div class="timeline-step">
              <div class="step-number">1</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Create the Database</h3>
                <p>In Notion, create a new page and add a database (table view)</p>
                <div class="code-block">
                  <pre><code>1. Open Notion
2. Click "+ New Page"
3. Type "/table" and select "Table - Inline"
4. Name it "My Network" or "Personal CRM"</code></pre>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-step">
              <div class="step-number">2</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Add Properties</h3>
                <p>Click "+ Add a property" and create these fields:</p>
                <div class="properties-list">
                  <div class="property-item">
                    <span class="prop-name">Name</span>
                    <span class="prop-type">Title (default)</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="property-item">
                    <span class="prop-name">Company</span>
                    <span class="prop-type">Text</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="property-item">
                    <span class="prop-name">Type</span>
                    <span class="prop-type">Select → Add options: Job Lead, Client, Mentor, Peer</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="property-item">
                    <span class="prop-name">Status</span>
                    <span class="prop-type">Select → Add: Active, Pending, Closed, Archived</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="property-item">
                    <span class="prop-name">Last Contact</span>
                    <span class="prop-type">Date</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="property-item">
                    <span class="prop-name">Next Follow-up</span>
                    <span class="prop-type">Date</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="property-item">
                    <span class="prop-name">Email</span>
                    <span class="prop-type">Email</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="property-item">
                    <span class="prop-name">LinkedIn</span>
                    <span class="prop-type">URL</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="property-item">
                    <span class="prop-name">Notes</span>
                    <span class="prop-type">Text</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-step">
              <div class="step-number">3</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Create Custom Views</h3>
                <p>Click "+ Add a view" to create filtered perspectives:</p>
                
                <div class="views-grid">
                  <div class="view-card">
                    <h4>📌 Active Contacts</h4>
                    <p><strong>Filter:</strong> Status = Active</p>
                    <p><strong>Sort:</strong> Next Follow-up (ascending)</p>
                    <p><strong>Use:</strong> Daily check-in</p>
                  </div>

                  <div class="view-card">
                    <h4>⏰ Follow-ups Due</h4>
                    <p><strong>Filter:</strong> Next Follow-up ≤ Today + 7 days</p>
                    <p><strong>Sort:</strong> Next Follow-up (ascending)</p>
                    <p><strong>Use:</strong> Weekly planning</p>
                  </div>

                  <div class="view-card">
                    <h4>💼 Job Search</h4>
                    <p><strong>Filter:</strong> Type = Job Lead</p>
                    <p><strong>Group by:</strong> Status</p>
                    <p><strong>Use:</strong> Track applications</p>
                  </div>

                  <div class="view-card">
                    <h4>📦 Archive</h4>
                    <p><strong>Filter:</strong> Status = Archived</p>
                    <p><strong>Sort:</strong> Last Contact (descending)</p>
                    <p><strong>Use:</strong> Reference only</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-step">
              <div class="step-number">4</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Add Your First Contacts</h3>
                <p>Start with 5-10 recent connections to test the system</p>
                <div class="example-entry">
                  <h4>Example Entry:</h4>
                  <div class="entry-data">
                    <p><strong>Name:</strong> Sarah Chen</p>
                    <p><strong>Company:</strong> TechCorp</p>
                    <p><strong>Type:</strong> Mentor</p>
                    <p><strong>Status:</strong> Active</p>
                    <p><strong>Last Contact:</strong> Apr 28, 2026 (Coffee chat about career paths)</p>
                    <p><strong>Next Follow-up:</strong> May 28, 2026 (Monthly check-in)</p>
                    <p><strong>Notes:</strong> Recommended I learn React. Offered to review my portfolio. Mentioned they're hiring interns in Q3.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section fade-in-up stagger-5">
          <h2>My Daily Workflow</h2>

          <div class="workflow-steps">
            <div class="workflow-card">
              <div class="workflow-time">☀️ Morning (5 min)</div>
              <h3>Quick Review</h3>
              <ol>
                <li>Open "Follow-ups Due" view</li>
                <li>Check who needs contact this week</li>
                <li>Block time on calendar for outreach</li>
              </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="workflow-card">
              <div class="workflow-time">📧 After Meeting/Event (2 min)</div>
              <h3>Add New Contact</h3>
              <ol>
                <li>Create new entry immediately</li>
                <li>Add key details from conversation</li>
                <li>Set follow-up date (usually 1-2 weeks)</li>
                <li>Draft quick LinkedIn connection request</li>
              </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="workflow-card">
              <div class="workflow-time">🌙 End of Week (15 min)</div>
              <h3>Weekly Maintenance</h3>
              <ol>
                <li>Update statuses (Active → Archived if no response)</li>
                <li>Add notes from the week's conversations</li>
                <li>Plan next week's outreach (3-5 people)</li>
                <li>Archive closed opportunities</li>
              </ol>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="callout callout-info">
            <strong>Time Investment:</strong> 5 min daily + 15 min weekly = ~40 min/month to maintain relationships that could change your career
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section fade-in-up">
          <h2>Follow-up Email Templates</h2>
          
          <div class="templates-section">
            <div class="template-box">
              <h3>Template 1: Post-Event Follow-up</h3>
              <div class="template-content">
                <p><strong>Subject:</strong> Great meeting you at [Event Name]</p>
                <pre><code>Hi [Name],

It was great connecting with you at [Event] yesterday! I really enjoyed our conversation about [specific topic you discussed].

[Insert 1-2 sentences referencing something specific they said or you learned]

I'd love to stay in touch and [reason: learn more about X / explore Y / continue the conversation]. Would you be open to a quick 20-minute virtual coffee in the next few weeks?

Looking forward to keeping in touch!

Best,
[Md Shahnawaz Hussain]</code></pre>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="template-box">
              <h3>Template 2: Monthly Check-in</h3>
              <div class="template-content">
                <p><strong>Subject:</strong> Quick check-in + [something relevant to them]</p>
                <pre><code>Hi [Name],

Hope you're doing well! I saw [article/news/post about their company or interest] and thought of you – [brief comment on why].

[Optional: Share a quick update about yourself in 1-2 sentences]

Would love to catch up sometime if you have 20 minutes. No pressure if you're swamped!

Best,
[Md Shahnawaz Hussain]</code></pre>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="template-box">
              <h3>Template 3: Adding Value</h3>
              <div class="template-content">
                <p><strong>Subject:</strong> Thought this might interest you</p>
                <pre><code>Hi [Name],

I came across [resource/article/person/opportunity] and immediately thought of you based on our conversation about [topic].

[Link or brief description]

No response needed – just wanted to share!

Hope all is well,
[Md Shahnawaz Hussain]</code></pre>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section fade-in-up">
          <h2>Advanced Tips & Automations</h2>

          <div class="tips-grid">
            <div class="tip-card">
              <h3>🔔 Notion Reminders</h3>
              <p>Set up database reminders for follow-ups:</p>
              <ol>
                <li>Click the "Next Follow-up" date property</li>
                <li>Enable "Remind me" → choose "On date of event"</li>
                <li>Get Notion notification when follow-up is due</li>
              </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="tip-card">
              <h3>📊 Track Metrics</h3>
              <p>Add these properties to see patterns:</p>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Response Rate:</strong> Formula to track who responds</li>
                <li><strong>Days Since Contact:</strong> Auto-calculate staleness</li>
                <li><strong>Total Interactions:</strong> Number property</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="tip-card">
              <h3>🔗 Link to Opportunities</h3>
              <p>Create separate databases for:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Job Applications → Link to recruiter contact</li>
                <li>Freelance Projects → Link to client</li>
                <li>Use Notion relations to connect them</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="tip-card">
              <h3>📱 Mobile Access</h3>
              <p>Download Notion mobile app:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Add contacts immediately after meetings</li>
                <li>Check follow-ups while commuting</li>
                <li>Update notes on-the-go</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="results-section fade-in-up">
          <h2>My 3-Month Results</h2>

          <div class="results-stats">
            <div class="stat-box">
              <div class="stat-number">43</div>
              <div class="stat-label">Contacts Added</div>
              <div class="stat-detail">15 active, 12 job leads, 3 clients, 13 archived</div>
            </div>

            <div class="stat-box">
              <div class="stat-number">87%</div>
              <div class="stat-label">Follow-up Rate</div>
              <div class="stat-detail">vs. ~30% before CRM</div>
            </div>

            <div class="stat-box">
              <div class="stat-number">2</div>
              <div class="stat-label">Freelance Clients</div>
              <div class="stat-detail">Both from warm introductions tracked in CRM</div>
            </div>

            <div class="stat-box">
              <div class="stat-number">4</div>
              <div class="stat-label">Interviews Secured</div>
              <div class="stat-detail">3 from follow-ups, 1 from cold outreach</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-viz">
            <h3>Growth Over Time</h3>
            <div class="chart-container">
              <canvas id="growthChart"></canvas>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Conclusion -->
        <section class="post-conclusion">
          <h2>Get Started Today</h2>
          <p>
            Building this CRM took me 30 minutes. Maintaining it takes 5 minutes a day. 
            The ROI? Two freelance clients, four interviews, and relationships I would have lost without a system.
          </p>
          
          <div class="next-steps">
            <h3>Your Action Plan</h3>
            <ol>
              <li>Duplicate the template (link at top of post)</li>
              <li>Add 5 recent contacts to test the system</li>
              <li>Set up one follow-up for this week</li>
              <li>Commit to 5-minute daily reviews for one month</li>
            </ol>
            
            <div class="cta-buttons">
              <a href="https://notion.so/templates/your-template" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">
                Get Free Template →
              </a>
              <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Share Your Setup</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>

      <!-- Post Footer -->
      <footer class="post-footer">
        <div class="post-tags">
          <span class="tag-label">Tags:</span>
          <a href="/blog?tag=tutorial" class="tag">Tutorial</a>
          <a href="/blog?tag=productivity" class="tag">Productivity</a>
          <a href="/blog?tag=notion" class="tag">Notion</a>
          <a href="/blog?tag=networking" class="tag">Networking</a>
          <a href="/blog?tag=career" class="tag">Career</a>
        </div>

        <div class="post-share">
          <span class="share-label">Share this post:</span>
          <a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Building a Personal CRM in Notion&url=https://yourblog.com/blog/notion-personal-crm" target="_blank" class="share-btn">Twitter</a>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/sharing/share-offsite/?url=https://yourblog.com/blog/notion-personal-crm" target="_blank" class="share-btn">LinkedIn</a>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
/* Template Preview */
.template-preview {
  max-width: 1000px;
  margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl);
  padding: var(--space-xl);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.05), rgba(78, 205, 196, 0.05));
  border: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
}

.preview-badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--space-xs);
  padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
  background: var(--color-primary);
  color: var(--color-bg);
  border-radius: 50px;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
}

.badge-icon {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
}

.preview-content {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
  gap: var(--space-xl);
  align-items: start;
}

.mock-database {
  background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  overflow: hidden;
}

.db-header {
  padding: var(--space-md);
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}

.db-title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
}

.db-stats {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
}

.db-rows {
  padding: var(--space-sm);
}

.db-row {
  padding: var(--space-sm);
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 0.8fr 1fr;
  gap: var(--space-sm);
  align-items: center;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
}

.row-tag {
  padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
  border-radius: 3px;
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  text-align: center;
}

.row-tag.active {
  background: rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.2);
  color: var(--color-primary);
}

.row-tag.interview {
  background: rgba(255, 230, 109, 0.2);
  color: var(--color-accent-3);
}

.row-tag.archived {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
}

.row-date {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
}

.preview-cta h3 {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
}

.preview-cta ul {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
}

.preview-cta li {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  font-size: 0.95rem;
}

/* Problem/Solution Grid */
.problem-solution {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: var(--space-lg);
  margin: var(--space-lg) 0;
}

.problem, .solution {
  padding: var(--space-lg);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  border: 2px solid;
}

.problem {
  background: rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.05);
  border-color: var(--color-accent-1);
}

.solution {
  background: rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.05);
  border-color: var(--color-primary);
}

/* Structure Grid */
.structure-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  gap: var(--space-lg);
  margin: var(--space-lg) 0;
}

.structure-card {
  padding: var(--space-lg);
  background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}

.structure-card h3 {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  color: var(--color-primary);
}

.structure-card ul {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
}

.structure-card li {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
}

/* Build Timeline */
.build-timeline {
  margin: var(--space-xl) 0;
}

.timeline-step {
  display: flex;
  gap: var(--space-lg);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  position: relative;
}

.timeline-step:not(:last-child)::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  left: 20px;
  top: 50px;
  bottom: -40px;
  width: 2px;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-primary), rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.2));
}

.step-number {
  flex-shrink: 0;
  width: 40px;
  height: 40px;
  background: var(--color-primary);
  color: var(--color-bg);
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-weight: 800;
  font-size: 1.25rem;
}

.step-content {
  flex: 1;
}

.properties-list {
  margin: var(--space-md) 0;
}

.property-item {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: var(--space-sm);
  background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
}

.prop-name {
  font-weight: 600;
}

.prop-type {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: var(--color-accent-2);
}

/* Views Grid */
.views-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  gap: var(--space-md);
  margin: var(--space-md) 0;
}

.view-card {
  padding: var(--space-md);
  background: var(--color-bg);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}

.view-card h4 {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  font-size: 1rem;
}

.view-card p {
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
}

/* Example Entry */
.example-entry {
  margin: var(--space-md) 0;
  padding: var(--space-lg);
  background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
}

.entry-data p {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
}

/* Workflow Steps */
.workflow-steps {
  display: grid;
  gap: var(--space-lg);
  margin: var(--space-lg) 0;
}

.workflow-card {
  padding: var(--space-lg);
  background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}

.workflow-time {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
  background: var(--color-primary);
  color: var(--color-bg);
  border-radius: 3px;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
}

.workflow-card h3 {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
}

.workflow-card ol {
  padding-left: var(--space-lg);
}

.workflow-card li {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
}

/* Templates Section */
.templates-section {
  margin: var(--space-lg) 0;
}

.template-box {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  padding: var(--space-lg);
  background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}

.template-box h3 {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  color: var(--color-accent-2);
}

.template-content p {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
}

.template-content pre {
  background: var(--color-bg);
  padding: var(--space-md);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* Tips Grid */
.tips-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  gap: var(--space-lg);
  margin: var(--space-lg) 0;
}

.tip-card {
  padding: var(--space-lg);
  background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}

.tip-card h3 {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  font-size: 1.1rem;
}

.tip-card ul, .tip-card ol {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
}

/* Results Stats */
.results-stats {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: var(--space-lg);
  margin: var(--space-lg) 0;
}

.stat-box {
  padding: var(--space-lg);
  background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  text-align: center;
}

.stat-number {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 3rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--color-primary);
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
}

.stat-label {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
}

.stat-detail {
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
}

/* Timeline Visualization */
.timeline-viz {
  margin: var(--space-xl) 0;
}

.timeline-viz h3 {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
}

.chart-container {
  height: 300px;
  padding: var(--space-lg);
  background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}

/* Shared post styles */
.blog-post {
  padding: var(--space-2xl) 0;
}

.post-header {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl);
  text-align: center;
}

.post-meta {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--space-sm);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
}

.post-tag {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
  background: var(--color-primary);
  color: var(--color-bg);
  border-radius: 3px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  font-weight: 600;
}

.post-subtitle {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin: var(--space-lg) auto;
  max-width: 700px;
}

.post-content {
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.content-section {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
}

.content-section h2 {
  font-size: 2rem;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  padding-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
}

.callout {
  margin: var(--space-lg) 0;
  padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  border-left: 4px solid;
}

.callout-success {
  background: rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.1);
  border-color: var(--color-primary);
}

.callout-info {
  background: rgba(78, 205, 196, 0.1);
  border-color: var(--color-accent-2);
}

.post-conclusion {
  margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
  padding: var(--space-xl);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.05), rgba(78, 205, 196, 0.05));
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-primary);
}

.next-steps {
  margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  padding-top: var(--space-xl);
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}

.cta-buttons {
  display: flex;
  gap: var(--space-md);
  justify-content: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-top: var(--space-lg);
}

.post-footer {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: var(--space-2xl) auto 0;
  padding-top: var(--space-xl);
  border-top: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}

.post-tags {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--space-sm);
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
}

.tag-label {
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
}

.tag {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
  background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  border-radius: 3px;
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.tag:hover {
  background: var(--color-primary);
  color: var(--color-bg);
  border-color: var(--color-primary);
}

.post-share {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--space-sm);
}

.share-label {
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
}

.share-btn {
  padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
  background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.share-btn:hover {
  background: var(--color-primary);
  color: var(--color-bg);
  border-color: var(--color-primary);
}

/* Mobile Responsive */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .preview-content,
  .problem-solution,
  .structure-grid,
  .views-grid,
  .tips-grid,
  .results-stats {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  
  .cta-buttons {
    flex-direction: column;
  }
}
</style>

